txt.en: 'Talk to me to become a \qAlly\q with the men of the Entwash Vale.'
'\qAlly\q with the Men of the Entwash Vale, coming right up! Just don't make any jokes about fire, they are kind of sensitive.'
Ally of the Men of the Entwash Vale
Their town is toast, can you blame them for being untrusting of outsiders?
